Subject: 6V wipers after 12V conversion

I used the Wolfsburg West armature conversion when I converted my bus
to 12V. See it here:

http://www.wolfsburgwest.com/cart/DetailsList.cfm?ID=113955811B

I had to sand their armature a bit and spend some extra time adjusting
its fit, but it works great with my original SWF wiper motor.

Good luck!

Richard
